---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — Diamond Web Dev"
  description="Terms of service for Diamond Web Dev covering quotes, payments, intellectual property, and project work."
  stickyNav={false}
>
  <main class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-[1.2] tracking-tight mb-4">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white/45 text-sm">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-10">
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
        These terms govern the relationship between Diamond Web Dev ("we", "us") and any client or
        visitor ("you") who engages our services or uses this website. By contacting us or
        commissioning work, you agree to these terms.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          1. Our services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Diamond Web Dev provides custom web design and development services including, but not
          limited to: website design, front-end and back-end development, performance optimisation,
          SEO, and ongoing support. The exact scope of any project will be agreed in writing before
          work begins.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          2. Quotes and payments
        </h2>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="mt-[6px] shrink-0 w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
            <span class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              All quotes are provided in writing and are valid for
              <strong class="text-white font-semibold">30 days</strong> from the date issued.
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="mt-[6px] shrink-0 w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
            <span class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              A <strong class="text-white font-semibold">50% deposit</strong> is required before work
              begins, with the remaining balance due on project completion before final files or live
              deployment are handed over.
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="mt-[6px] shrink-0 w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
            <span class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              Invoices are payable within <strong class="text-white font-semibold">14 days</strong>.
              Late payments may incur interest in accordance with the Late Payment of Commercial
              Debts Act 1998.
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="mt-[6px] shrink-0 w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
            <span class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              Any work outside the agreed scope will be quoted separately and requires your written
              approval before proceeding.
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          3. Your responsibilities
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          To allow us to deliver your project effectively, you agree to:
        </p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="mt-[6px] shrink-0 w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
            <span class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              Provide all required content, images, copy, and access credentials in a timely manner
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="mt-[6px] shrink-0 w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
            <span class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              Ensure any content you supply does not infringe third-party copyright or other rights
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="mt-[6px] shrink-0 w-[6px] h-[6px] rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
            <span class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              Respond to feedback requests and sign-off requests within a reasonable timeframe to
              avoid project delays
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          4. Intellectual property
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          All design and code produced by Diamond Web Dev remains our intellectual property until
          final payment is received in full. Upon receipt of full payment, all rights to the
          completed work transfer to you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          We reserve the right to display completed work in our portfolio unless you request
          otherwise in writing before the project begins.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          5. Revisions
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          The number of included revision rounds will be specified in your project quote. Revisions
          are changes to the existing agreed design or functionality — they do not include new
          features or significant changes to scope, which will be quoted separately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          6. Cancellations
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          If you cancel a project after work has begun, the deposit is non-refundable. If work
          completed exceeds the value of the deposit at the point of cancellation, an invoice will
          be issued for the additional work completed to that date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          7. Limitation of liability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Diamond Web Dev will not be liable for any indirect or consequential loss, loss of
          revenue, or loss of data arising from the use of a delivered website. Our total liability
          for any claim is limited to the total amount paid by you for the specific project in
          question.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          8. Governing law
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          These terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes will be subject to
          the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">
          9. Questions
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          If you have any questions about these terms, get in touch at
          <a
            href="mailto:mikeydiamond@hotmail.co.uk"
            class="text-accent hover:text-[#64eca0] transition-colors"
            >mikeydiamond@hotmail.co.uk</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-accent hover:text-[#64eca0] transition-colors text-sm font-medium"
      >
        <svg
          width="16"
          height="16"
          viewBox="0 0 16 16"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            d="M13 8H3M3 8L7 4M3 8L7 12"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.75"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
        Back to home
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
